            <a href="https://github.com/rfallison25-cell/Test1/tree/main/3d-physics-simulation" class="btn">View on GitHub</a>
        </div>

        <footer>
            <p>💡 Computational Methods Final Project | Python | NumPy | Matplotlib | Three.js | Physics Simulation</p>
            <p>© 2026 rfallison25-cell</p>
